    "statementHTML": "<div class=\"statement-body\">\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-goal\">\n   <h2><span class=\"icon icon-goal\">&nbsp;</span><span>Goal </span></h2>\n   <span class=\"question-statement\">Milo is scanning long satellites ids printed on a paper strip and found a simple trick to be faster than Gary.<br>Instead of shifting the optical scanner head <var>k</var> characters at a time, he found out it is possible to hover its head continuously over the strip at high speed without confusing the OCR, provided any repeated character sequence is no longer than the head width.<br>When <var>k</var> is <const>0</const>, a sensor upgrade allows to scan the strip as is.<br><br>Given a string <var>s</var>, split any repeated character sequence longer than <var>k</var> with a <const>space</const> char in a greedy fashion (the <const>space</const> being put after the <var>k</var>th char).</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-protocol\">\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-input\"><strong>Line 1:</strong> A string <var>s</var> consisting of digits '0123456789'<br><strong>Line 2:</strong> An integer <var>k</var>, the width of the scanner head</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-output\"><var>s</var> with any <var>k+1</var> repeated char sequence split with a <const>space</const> char</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Constraints</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-constraints\">1 &le; length of <var>s</var> &le; <const>100</const><br><br>0 &le; <var>k</var> &le; 32</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Example</div>\n      <div class=\"statement-inout\">\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-in\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-in\">0001110000\n2</pre>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-out\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-out\">00 011 100 00</pre>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n   </div>\n</div>"
